Version:        1.8.2
Release:        0
Summary:        Advanced IRC Bouncer
License:        Apache-2.0
Group:          Productivity/Networking/IRC
URL:            https://wiki.znc.in/ZNC
Source0:        https://znc.in/releases/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
